title: Reward for bluefintuan's amazing contributions towards the community
body: This is a snapshot vote for our beloved community artist bluefintuan due to the amazing contributions which he has done towards the community. The rewards will be listed as follows. Please pick any reward which you deem fit for his work that he has done for the community! It will be airdropped to bluefintuan by the DAO wallet.
